Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.26,0:00:45.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.75,0:01:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的问题 还是直接去找本人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.62,0:01:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里沉睡着他的遗传基因
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.20,0:01:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且祭品还活着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.49,0:03:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来不像感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.69,0:03:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是午饭的关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系啦 昨天就有些不对劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.89,0:03:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修炼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍术修炼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.18,0:03:43.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们啊 鸣人的身体不适…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:47.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说好认真教我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.55,0:03:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶的英雄不过如此吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 你们听着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:03:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要战胜各种困难和挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是体力和运动能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.91,0:04:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.89,0:04:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但漫无目的地锻炼无益于实战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是…经过我的长年修炼 研究出一套方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名为 鸣人流强劲动力以及神奇训练
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听起来很带劲 哥哥也一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.96,0:04:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掌握了它 危难时刻你们也能大展身手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.48,0:04:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不喜欢太辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.38,0:04:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少抱怨了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.02,0:04:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论什么事 都需要百分百的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.78,0:04:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先飞奔到河边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真丢脸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.36,0:04:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:48.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说佯攻是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是连这都不懂的笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啊 我是说被兜利用真是太丢脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.72,0:05:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以不死之身为荣的你竟会被分尸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.59,0:05:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真够可怜的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还不是一样 自爆身亡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.67,0:05:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:10.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是为了终极艺术
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最崇高的自我献身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:16.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少狡辩 还不是挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.51,0:05:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.49,0:05:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 训练…结束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出了一身汗 真轻松啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:34.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.07,0:05:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去买些饮料来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.95,0:05:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.43,0:05:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 真不像样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.46,0:05:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天…身体不太舒服…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:06:59.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是英雄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁让你总是嚷着艺术 艺术的 烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.63,0:07:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽做些造型丑陋的炸弹 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那狗屁仪式才是又臭又长呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.09,0:07:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害得我还得挺身掩护你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.57,0:07:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不需要你掩护呢 冒牌的艺术家混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.32,0:07:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少叫嚣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.39,0:07:26.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没了那咒印 你一文不值
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.69,0:07:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就尝尝我的诅咒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计你会先被我的艺术给炸飞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.02,0:07:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,热身运动已经做过了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.16,0:08:14.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吃那边的冰激淋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.29,0:08:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.61,0:08:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好 干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧看吧 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.43,0:08:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛 很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.01,0:08:30.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.69,0:08:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.76,0:08:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:49.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.58,0:08:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.58,0:08:58.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.54,0:08:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想再见一面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.93,0:09:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.14,0:09:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.54,0:09:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是一直都在你们身边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.98,0:09:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然完全没减肥的概念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:23.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.46,0:09:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我伤势痊愈 一定会运动的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.34,0:09:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就由我严厉地指导你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.36,0:11:05.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也太夸张了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.75,0:11:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微休息下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掠夺 掠夺…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:43.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快出去…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:12:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快出去…快出去…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.49,0:11:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以啊 米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以对哥哥说这么过分的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.92,0:12:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被讨厌了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:20.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做错什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.89,0:13:22.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.14,0:13:25.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:27.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.26,0:13:29.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.96,0:13:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等…小樱…不用啦…那里…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.95,0:13:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这么担心你 跟傻瓜似的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.62,0:13:46.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…镇长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之为了尽快通知各位 就匆忙赶来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.43,0:14:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今早 这名老者徘徊于镇政厅之前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.88,0:14:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:05.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷…爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩都平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.28,0:14:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村长能平安归来才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.97,0:14:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛被刺伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我彷徨于荒野之时 总算得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.03,0:14:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多克 真是给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.05,0:14:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 怎么会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.99,0:14:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有件重要的事要问你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.10,0:14:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得那晚我给你的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.69,0:14:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许你已经察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.61,0:14:57.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是藏于村子祭坛里宝物的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为防被偷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.44,0:15:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将其拆散
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给了你及另一名守卫保管
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜的是 我和他保管的五根都被夺走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.01,0:15:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅剩的两根 无论如何都要保住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想把它交给迪索纳斯严加保管
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:42.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:45.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这么打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.04,0:15:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…剩下的东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的…那些…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷 你好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:08.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秽土转生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.98,0:16:11.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子真机灵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来很特别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:16.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被骗了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住那个胖子 拷问出情报来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:38.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.69,0:17:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:34.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半死不活的祭品看来派不上多大用场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:17:59.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掠夺 掠夺…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.15,0:19:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快出去 快出去…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:18:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米娜 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.70,0:19:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米娜 米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.92,0:19:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快出去 快出去…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.41,0:19:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快从鸣人哥哥的体内出去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.15,0:20:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九尾的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.69,0:20:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.65,0:22:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,5,,像你这样拥有强大力量的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.76,0:22:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,5,,无论将之用于正道或是邪道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.32,0:23:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,5,,都必须背负巨大的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.43,0:23:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,5,,但是你的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.19,0:23:05.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,5,,为何想要变强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.30,0:23:08.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,5,,下集 火影忍者疾风传
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.30,0:23:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,5,,力量 第四集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.44,0:23:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,5,,这份执念一定会指引你前进的
